{"tid":1077082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"慘！張超雄扭傷腰急症室等三個半鐘 坐輪椅開會去廁所都要人幫","createTime":"2019-03-25T10:42:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T19:07:42.000Z","uid":173208,"like":655,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":118,"replies":[{"pid":"7617a301b9bb30eaff9946f0bc3faa4755a9e8cb","tid":1077082,"uid":173208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T10:42:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190324/s00001/1553408994029/【emily-online】張超雄傷腰坐輪椅-原來等港鐵用板要等四班車\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190324%2Fs00001%2F1553408994029%2F%E3%80%90emily-online%E3%80%91%E5%BC%B5%E8%B6%85%E9%9B%84%E5%82%B7%E8%85%B0%E5%9D%90%E8%BC%AA%E6%A4%85-%E5%8E%9F%E4%BE%86%E7%AD%89%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E7%94%A8%E6%9D%BF%E8%A6%81%E7%AD%89%E5%9B%9B%E7%8F%AD%E8%BB%8A&d=Fb7z1ilWoLc7MobAJ3fbq6%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=13780ec5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190324%2Fs00001%2F1553408994029%2F%E3%80%90emily-online%E3%80%91%E5%BC%B5%E8%B6%85%E9%9B%84%E5%82%B7%E8%85%B0%E5%9D%90%E8%BC%AA%E6%A4%85-%E5%8E%9F%E4%BE%86%E7%AD%89%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E7%94%A8%E6%9D%BF%E8%A6%81%E7%AD%89%E5%9B%9B%E7%8F%AD%E8%BB%8A&h=6e83fc31\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190324/s00001/1553408994029/【emily-online】張超雄傷腰坐輪椅-原來等港鐵用板要等四班車</a> <br />\n<br />\n【Emily Online】張超雄傷腰坐輪椅：原來等港鐵用板要等四班車 (15:55)<br />\n<br />\n工黨立法會議員張超雄扭親條腰接近一星期，去立法會開會時要輪椅代步。今日（24日）凌晨，佢喺fb專頁分享感受，話呢幾日令佢更加體會病人同殘疾人士嘅困苦，仲好感慨咁話：「健康的人真的不明白病人的困苦；飽肚人不明肚餓人的愁。這個社會，都是為健康和飽肚人而建造的。」<br />\n<br />\n張超雄噚日去咗長毛介梁國雄紹嘅中醫師求診，一去就成個下晝，初嘗坐輪椅，佢發現殘疾人士出入遇到嘅難處，「原來地鐵車廂和月台的隙縫是如此闊，對電動輪椅做（造）成危險；原來要等地鐵職員用板要等上四班車。」一次就診就令到佢疲累不堪，「這些都是我以前認知的，但發生在自己身上，真是有另一種知（滋）味」。<br />\n<br />\n張超雄又話佢喺屋企行咗幾分鐘已經好攰，「我以為自己有的能力，和現實竟然有這麼大的距離！對於自己身體狀況的衰退，實在很難接受！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/03/24/DHYXvw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F03%2F24%2FDHYXvw.jpg&h=665c964e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/03/24/bKkSWl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F03%2F24%2FbKkSWl.jpg&h=3ee46221&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"459caca52ad96b765647771bba03304ecb0a5b7b","tid":1077082,"uid":402,"like":442,"dislike":5,"score":437,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T10:44:38.000Z","msg":"未夠慘喎"},{"pid":"71592dfa56e38e7c138a00e2d7ca73bd94acd0d5","tid":1077082,"uid":30063,"like":381,"dislike":8,"score":373,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T10:45:13.000Z","msg":"快撚D死啦 含家剷"},{"pid":"6f32196764444abcfabe6db2b7b220ecacd3691d","tid":1077082,"uid":131078,"like":141,"dislike":1,"score":140,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T10:45:47.000Z","msg":"祝佢長命百歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b4c331bc6da253e97ca6ad4faeedde53d21e8d","tid":1077082,"uid":35014,"like":333,"dislike":5,"score":328,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T10:46:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ef8c2de86e5259f1f3c8009411940a47c894d69","tid":1077082,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T10:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44fa19a15bf0dcdd87b44d1512763001b6652f51","tid":1077082,"uid":79919,"like":141,"dislike":3,"score":138,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:00:21.000Z","msg":"點解唔去輪吓政府街症， 再等轉骨科， 等下等下可以睇埋深切治療<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face